<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比放学后去了体育馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面在下雨，所以，今天儿童中心在室内活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他希望可以去外面玩儿，他还希望自己带了点心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他饿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天大家看上去都很累。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们做点东西吃吧。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我妈妈累的时候会喝咖啡。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师大笑起来。“我们要做比咖啡更好的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要做我们自己的儿童中心能量棒。大家都过来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太酷了。我们要自己做点心了！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要把食材混合起来。黑板上有说明。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一步：把一罐炼乳和两汤匙的油倒进碗里，搅拌。” 雪莉老师念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜拿起一个打开的罐头。“炼乳在这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我准备油。” 贾森加了两汤匙的油。“搅拌！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第二步：加两杯烤燕麦片，搅拌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜拿起一袋烤燕麦片。“两杯是多少？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比给她一个量杯。“装两次。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一、二。好了！” 尼娜笑了，“真好玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第三步：加一杯膨化小麦，搅拌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森加了一杯膨化小麦。“真酷。这很简单。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第四步：加半杯杏仁片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杏仁片在哪里呢，雪莉老师？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，莉琪，杏仁片在这里。” 雪莉老师给了她一袋杏仁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪把杏仁加了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第五步：加点甜味。加入巧克力碎和葡萄干。” 尼娜念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我最喜欢葡萄干了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别忘了第六步：加一杯葵花籽。” 雪莉老师提醒大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别忘了搅拌、搅拌、搅拌哦！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在搅拌、搅拌、搅拌！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“铺在抹好油的烤盘上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要怎么给烤盘抹油呢，雪莉老师？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在纸巾上倒一些油。” 她回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后抹在烤盘上。” 雪莉老师给了他一张纸巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我们要这样压一压食材。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师用力压了压食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以烤了！” 雪莉老师把烤盘放进烤箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用175摄氏度烤25分钟。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那这25分钟我们做什么呢？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们踢足球吧。女生对男生！” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！男生赢了！” 贾森和波比很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……我闻到了香味儿！” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我们的点心！” 雪莉老师说，“要做最后一步了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“切成小条后品尝。” 波比念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就是可以吃了！我觉得室内活动也挺不错的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师切了12个小条。每个人都吃了一个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。我们做的点心真好吃！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。现在我有力气了。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们再去踢足球吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>